---
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Faq from "@components/faq.astro";
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Approach">
    <Container>
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-8 mt-12 dark:text-gray-200">
            <img
                class="mt-2 mb-8 w-auto"
                src="/devops.jpg"
                alt="devops"
                loading="lazy"
            />
            <h1
                class="text-4xl mb-2 lg:text-5xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight mt-1 lg:leading-tight dark:text-white"
            >
                Approach
            </h1>
            <p class="mb-8 dark:text-gray-200">
                At Lockstrom, our approach is built on clarity, precision, and
                results.
            </p>

            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
            >
                Clarity
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-8 dark:text-gray-200">
                We operate with full transparency—clear documentation,
                predictable timelines, and open channels for feedback. Our
                clients are never left guessing. Every milestone is tracked,
                every decision documented, and every deliverable backed by
                accountability.
            </p>
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
            >
                Precision
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-8 dark:text-gray-200">
                Every engagement begins with a deep understanding of your
                operational goals, constraints, and success metrics. Whether
                you're modernizing legacy infrastructure or launching a new
                digital service, we align our solutions with your mission from
                day one.
            </p>
            <h2
                class="text-2xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
            >
                Results
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-8 dark:text-gray-200">
                Lockstrom combines agile methodologies with rigorous planning to
                deliver fast, iterative results without sacrificing quality. We
                prototype early, test often, and refine continuously—so your
                stakeholders see progress, not promises.
            </p>
            <h2
                class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold leading-10 tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
            >
                Why Agencies Choose Lockstrom
            </h2>
            <ul
                class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 xl:mt-2"
            >
                <li>U.S.-based development team</li>
                <li>Experience with procurement workflows and compliance</li>
                <li>Clean, audit-ready code and documentation</li>
                <li>
                    Flexible engagement models for short and long-term projects
                </li>
                <li>
                    Proven ability to deliver under tight timelines and complex
                    scopes
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </Container>
</Layout>
